---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Vulgarisation Scientifique | Alain Didier Noutchegueme">
  <div class="fixed top-0 inset-x-0 h-[800px] bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50/60 via-purple-50/10 to-transparent z-[-2] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="fixed inset-0 z-[-1] opacity-[0.015] pointer-events-none mix-blend-overlay" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=%220 0 200 200%22 xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%3E%3Cfilter id=%22noiseFilter%22%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=%22fractalNoise%22 baseFrequency=%220.8%22 numOctaves=%223%22 stitchTiles=%22stitch%22/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=%22100%25%22 height=%22100%25%22 filter=%22url(%23noiseFilter)%22/%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>

  <main class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    
    <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/" class="group inline-flex items-center text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-900 mb-16 transition-colors uppercase">
      <svg class="w-3 h-3 mr-2 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-all" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" /></svg>
      Retour à l'accueil
    </a>

    <header class="mb-20 max-w-[700px]">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-zinc-900 tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6">
        Vulgarisation Scientifique
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[1.1rem] text-zinc-600 leading-[1.8] font-light border-l-[1.5px] border-zinc-300 pl-6">
        Démocratiser l'abstraction. Des formats courts d'une page conçus pour extraire l'essence de concepts complexes sans en sacrifier la rigueur mathématique.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-16">

      <article class="border border-zinc-200/60 rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/40">
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 bg-zinc-50/80 border-b border-zinc-200/60 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest bg-white border border-zinc-200 px-2 py-1 rounded-md">Santé & Géométrie Spectrale</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest">26 Mai 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-900">Peut-on entendre une tumeur ?</h2>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/tumeur.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-all shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" /></svg>
            Télécharger le PDF
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full h-[600px] md:h-[900px] bg-zinc-100 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8 z-0">
            <p class="text-zinc-500 font-light mb-4">Votre navigateur mobile empêche l'aperçu direct de ce document.</p>
            <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/tumeur.pdf" class="text-blue-600 font-medium underline">Ouvrir le document</a>
          </div>
          <iframe 
            src="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/tumeur.pdf#toolbar=0&view=FitH" 
            class="w-full h-full relative z-10 border-0" 
            title="Aperçu : Peut-on entendre une tumeur ?">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="border border-zinc-200/60 rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/40">
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 bg-zinc-50/80 border-b border-zinc-200/60 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest bg-white border border-zinc-200 px-2 py-1 rounded-md">Épidémiologie Mathématique</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest">28 Avril 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-900">La dérivée au sens d'Atangana-Baleanu et le moustique</h2>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/moustique.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-all shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" /></svg>
            Télécharger le PDF
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full h-[600px] md:h-[900px] bg-zinc-100 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8 z-0">
            <p class="text-zinc-500 font-light mb-4">Votre navigateur mobile empêche l'aperçu direct de ce document.</p>
            <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/moustique.pdf" class="text-blue-600 font-medium underline">Ouvrir le document</a>
          </div>
          <iframe 
            src="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/moustique.pdf#toolbar=0&view=FitH" 
            class="w-full h-full relative z-10 border-0" 
            title="Aperçu : La dérivée d'Atangana-Baleanu">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </article>


      <article class="border border-zinc-200/60 rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/40">
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 bg-zinc-50/80 border-b border-zinc-200/60 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest bg-white border border-zinc-200 px-2 py-1 rounded-md">Analyse Non-Lisse</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest">24 Mars 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-900">Au-delà du gradient : La dérivée au sens de Clarke</h2>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/clarke.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-all shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" /></svg>
            Télécharger le PDF
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full h-[600px] md:h-[900px] bg-zinc-100 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8 z-0">
            <p class="text-zinc-500 font-light mb-4">Votre navigateur mobile empêche l'aperçu direct de ce document.</p>
            <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/clarke.pdf" class="text-blue-600 font-medium underline">Ouvrir le document</a>
          </div>
          <iframe 
            src="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/clarke.pdf#toolbar=0&view=FitH" 
            class="w-full h-full relative z-10 border-0" 
            title="Aperçu : La dérivée de Clarke">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="border border-zinc-200/60 rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/40">
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 bg-zinc-50/80 border-b border-zinc-200/60 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest bg-white border border-zinc-200 px-2 py-1 rounded-md">Optimisation de Forme</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest">27 Février 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-900">La dérivée de forme d'un domaine et le marcheur ivre</h2>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/marcheur.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-all shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" /></svg>
            Télécharger le PDF
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full h-[600px] md:h-[900px] bg-zinc-100 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8 z-0">
            <p class="text-zinc-500 font-light mb-4">Votre navigateur mobile empêche l'aperçu direct de ce document.</p>
            <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/marcheur.pdf" class="text-blue-600 font-medium underline">Ouvrir le document</a>
          </div>
          <iframe 
            src="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/marcheur.pdf#toolbar=0&view=FitH" 
            class="w-full h-full relative z-10 border-0" 
            title="Aperçu : La dérivée de forme">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </article>


      <article class="border border-zinc-200/60 rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/40">
        <div class="p-6 md:p-8 bg-zinc-50/80 border-b border-zinc-200/60 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest bg-white border border-zinc-200 px-2 py-1 rounded-md">Modélisation Mathématique</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest">28 Janvier 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-900">L'art de mettre le monde en équation</h2>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/equation.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-all shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" /></svg>
            Télécharger le PDF
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full h-[600px] md:h-[900px] bg-zinc-100 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8 z-0">
            <p class="text-zinc-500 font-light mb-4">Votre navigateur mobile empêche l'aperçu direct de ce document.</p>
            <a href="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/equation.pdf" class="text-blue-600 font-medium underline">Ouvrir le document</a>
          </div>
          <iframe 
            src="/Alain-Didier-Noutchegueme/equation.pdf#toolbar=0&view=FitH" 
            class="w-full h-full relative z-10 border-0" 
            title="Aperçu : Mettre le monde en équation">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>